      "title": "Build a Smart World with CHCNAV Precision Solutions",
      "description": "CHCNAV delivers high-precision navigation, positioning, and mapping solutions for surveying, construction, marine, agriculture, and autonomous systems worldwide.",
      "text_excerpt": "Build a Smart World with CHCNAV Precision Solutions\nBuilding a Smart World with CHC Navigation Precision Solutions\nSmarter Precision in Every World\nEmpower your daily operations with our advanced mapping, positioning, and navigation solutions.\nHOME_BUTTON\nScroll\nScroll\nGEOSPATIAL\nCHC Navigation is a leader in the geospatial industry, delivering advanced geospatial technology that transforms mapping and surveying. Our geospatial solutions integrate GNSS, LiDAR, UAV, and USV systems to achieve high-precision results. Designed for professionals, CHCNAV empowers smarter decisions and sustainable development through geospatial innovation.\nGo to Geospatial\nMACHINE CONTROL\nCHC Navigation delivers advanced machine control solutions that improve precision, productivity, and efficiency in earthmoving. Our GPS machine control systems for excavators, dozers, graders, and compactors are complemented by GNSS rovers and CAD field software empowering your jobsite to stay on schedule and within spec.\nGo to Machine Control\nNAVIGATION\nWe lead innovation in GNSS navigation with hybrid GNSS+INS technologies built for unmanned systems, robotics, and autonomous vehicles. CHC Navigation GPS RTK sensors and chipsets enable high-accuracy, reliable performance for integrators in automotive, logistics, mining, and construction, powering scalable autonomous navigation applications.\nGo to Navigation\nAGRICULTURE\nImprove your precision agriculture practices with smart agriculture solutions built for farms of any size. CHC Navigation’s tractor guidance and auto-steering systems, powered by GPS farming technologies, optimize planting, irrigation, and harvesting, helping you increase yields, cut costs, and drive sustainability across every stage of their operation.\nGo to Agriculture\nEXPLORE OUR SOLUTIONS\nInnovating Global Navigation & Mapping Solutions\nCHC Navigation is advancing mapping, navigation, and positioning technologies. We are boosting efficiency and affordability in geospatial, digital construction, precision agriculture, and navigation industries. Our commitment to innovation makes CHCNAV your trustworthy partner, offering personalized support and solutions worldwide.\nLearn More\nyears of innovation​\nglobal experts\ncountries served worldwide\nR&D Engineers\nLATEST NEWS\nGeospatial\nApr 17, 2026\nWhat Is RTK GPS and How Does It Improve Positioning Accuracy?\nLearn More\nGeospatial\nApr 10, 2026\nA Smarter Indoor Survey Workflow: Handheld SLAM Scanning with the CHCNAV RS7\nLearn More\nGeospatial\nApr 9, 2026\nCHC Navigation Launches AlphaAir 6, a Long-Range Airborne LiDAR System for UAV Mapping and Aerial Surveying\nLearn More\nGeospatial\nApr 8, 2026\nCHC Navigation Confirms Readiness for Upcoming BeiDou System Upgrade\nLearn More\nGeospatial\nApr 2, 2026\nHow to Choose the Right Land Surveying Equipment for Your Project\nLearn More\nGeospatial\nMar 31, 2026\nCHC Navigation Announces Major Updates to i93, i85, i76 and iBase GNSS Receivers\nLearn More\nAgriculture\nMar 25, 2026\nOne Terminal, Unlimit"
